@node Install "Installation"
                                 @{b}Installation@{ub}
                                ==============

A.Use The Auto Installer..(if there is one).


B.Copy  Txt2Pdf_gui to Where ever you want as long as you have Txt2Pdf in System:c/


C.If you dont have Txt2Pdf in system:c/  than run txt2pdf_gui & click on download to get latest
version of txt2pdf.lha in to ram than install..

Or

fireup your browser http://www.biozombie.centelia.net/portacall/

@endnode




@node usage "usage"
                                 @{b}Usage@{ub}
           (-) - >

               - > Double click on Txt2Pdf_gui
               - >
               - > Select_a_file  =  txt file
               - >
               - > Select_a_Font  =  fonts plz

               - > Select_Font_Size = min=6 & max=50 for now
                   -------------
               - > Than click on Convert Job Done.......

               - ---------------


               - Download Button will download txt2Pdf.lha file from my own site...




@endnode

